ion','Azyk önümçiliginiň döwrebap tehnologiýalarynyň \"Agro-Pak Türkmenistan-2023\" atly halkara segisi','images/2023-03-03/i3jV8j2fa7f6fJVwFt78f1XmNx5zCVOGfoUSXqJz.jpg','28.11.2023 - 30.11.2023','2023-03-03 17:27:25','2023-03-03 17:27:25'),(58,'Выставка экспортных товаров Турецкой Республики','Exhibition of export goods of the Republic of Turkey','Türkiýe Respublikasynyň eksport harytlarynyň sergisi','images/2023-03-03/qHfKF33m5WsbNDUIr5Tv8PInG1XMX8sp898rbrBt.jpg','06.12.2023 - 08.12.2023','2023-03-03 17:30:04','2023-03-03 17:30:04');
